description: Israel deployed drones and bulldozers amid one of the deadliest recent raids on the West Bank city.
maintext: Israeli-Palestinian tensions in the West Bank, which were already high, have been fuelled further by the war in Gaza, which began after an unprecedented deadly attack on Israel by Hamas gunmen on 7 October. More than 150 Palestinians and three Israelis have been killed in the West Bank since the war began.
title: Jenin raid: 14 Palestinians killed in clashes in West Bank city
